OL,3,CPony and trap crash in Kent leaves man
OL,4,Cand young girl dead and woman critical
OL,6,FA man and a young girl travelling in a
OL,7,Fpony and trap have died following a
OL,8,Fcrash involving a tipper truck in Kent.
OL,10,FPolice say emergency services were
OL,11,Fcalled to the A228 Boyle Way, between
OL,12,Fthe junctions of Bandridges Road and
OL,13,FHale Street, in East Peckham near
OL,14,FTonbridge at 6.25pm on Wednesday. (1
OL,15,FApril)
OL,17,FA white DAF tipper truck was being
OL,18,Fdriven on the northbound carriageway
OL,19,Fwhen it was involved in a collision
OL,20,Fwith a pony and trap travelling in the
OL,21,Fsame direction.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
