OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1775235955
OL,3,CPony and trap crash in Kent leaves man
OL,4,Cand young girl dead and woman critical
OL,6,FA man who was in the trap died at the
OL,7,Fscene.
OL,9,FA woman and young girl who had also
OL,10,Fbeen riding in the trap were taken
OL,11,Fhospital. The young girl was confirmed
OL,12,Fdead at hospital and the woman remains
OL,13,Fin a critical condition.
OL,15,FThe pony also died at the scene.
OL,17,FThe driver of the tipper, a 29-year-
OL,18,Fold man from Kent, was arrested in
OL,19,Fconnection with the incident and was
OL,20,Ftaken into custody.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
