OL,3,CPony and trap crash in Kent leaves man
OL,4,Cand young girl dead and woman critical
OL,6,FA Kent Police spokesperson said: "An
OL,7,Finvestigation into the circumstances
OL,8,Fis underway and witnesses or anyone
OL,9,Fwho saw the truck or pony and trap
OL,10,Fprior to the collision, is urged to
OL,11,Fcontact the appeal line.
OL,13,F"Call the Serious Collision
OL,14,FInvestigation Unit on 01622 798538,
OL,15,Fquoting reference BN/JG/027/26."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
